{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no questions about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How could these guys dare tell me, people, my family that was for generations in Germany-- I'm at least as much German as anybody else-- how can they dare to tell me that I can't go to my beloved concerts or my beloved soccer games.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so, therefore, I did that with that pin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so, with the help of a briefcase-- that almost every man carries over there and carried over there and still does, I see-- I covered this up.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When it came to a point to take it off, and took it off secretly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I had, I had my own gimmick, very, very easily trained.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was very quick with this thing, took it off, had the brief case in front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it started-- when I would take it off-- slid right into the side pocket of my coat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I reversed the procedure when I came home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at the slave labor, I worked until I was finally picked up to be sent to the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was about in 1943-- in March of 1943-- when Hitler announced, in big headlines in the newspapers and over the radio, congratulations to the German population.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We now can tell you that 90% of the Jews of Germany and other areas have been-- and use the word-- 'evacuated.'",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "90%.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The great mathematician that I was, I figured, my gosh, 10%?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I belong to the 10% that are still here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we also heard now news about Hitler's successes-- or lack of successes on the fronts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we figured, my gosh, now the Allies really having starting to return.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was just a time, I guess, when Hitler was-- his troops were thrown back from the Russian front, somewhat.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
